On Base Percentage (OBP): Is it the best? And why it obviously is?

Rodrigo Motoyama

08/03/2020

Introduction

Following my first publication, I would like to talk about one of my favorite batting statistics, OBP or On Base Percentage. Hopefully after reading this you will get hooked up on OBP as me :). I intend to cover what OBP means and measures, why it is a good statistic, where it fails, and why I think it is better than others like avg (batting average) and slg (slugging). So bear with me and let’s dive in to it.
